Plot: MALCOLM FUNCE'S BUSINESS IS BRINGING NAIVE BRITISH AND IRISH ACTORS TO LA FOR HIS "INDUSTRY NETWORKING WEEK" - EVEN THOUGH HE KNOWS NO-ONE AND HAS NO CLUE - IN A CITY WHERE ANYTHING IS POSSIBLE.
Title: Breaking Hollywood: One Actor at a Time
Actors: Emrhys Cooper, Jenny Dixon, Liam Alex Heffron, Alastair James Murden
